items.title: TRUE ESSENCE
items.description:
This collection is imbued with an intoxicating array of wildly fantastical colors, which transform ordinary vistas into the realms of otherworldly creatures. Each artwork deliberately obscures the line between good and evil, leaving viewers in suspense‚Äîuncertain whether they're beholding a charmingly whimsical character or a monster poised to unleash its venom at any moment‚Ä¶

This collection comes from Koozma Corbut, an artist who combines classical photography with modern visualization technologies to enrich his pieces with deep emotional resonance and cutting-edge visual flair.

In Q2 2024, buyers of NFTs will gain access to a service enabling them to download high-resolution originals of artworks. This addition will allow owners to physically print their digital pieces at any print shop, bringing Koozma Corbut's vibrant and fantastical creations from the digital realm into the tangible world. The link to the service will appear on his Instagram (https://www.instagram.com/koozma_corbut/), so stay tuned for updates!

items.title: RING
items.description:
Welcome to "Ring" - the blockchain game that's more addictive than your favorite online quests and crypto investments combined!
We've cooked up mechanics so intuitive even a n00b could get it, all wrapped up in a plot juicier than a crypto pump and dump.
Each NFT character in the "Ring" universe is as unique as your rarest loot drop, with their own style, stats, and snarky one-liners.
From lucky breaks to risky moves, every hero's got their perks and pitfalls, so choose wisely: do you chase fast gains or opt for safety and stability?
Team up with your crew to stack those sats and level up together - because let's face it, solo play is for NPCs.
With plot twists unfolding across Europe's finest cities, your wit, cunning, and maybe just a dash of luck will be the keys to untangling our most mind-bending puzzles yet.
Our goal? Equip you with everything you need to pwn the game and reach those sweet, sweet achievements. See you in the Ring üòè
